<@U12A55KGW|yabo23> has joined the channel

<@U061HDV96>: for activity results if they are very small I handle them there, if they need some kind of decision making then I pass an enum to my presenter indicating what happened. For onPause, onResume etc. I avoid having any lifecycle callbacks in my presenters and instead I naming the function based on what happends. For example if I wanted to always unsub from Rx subscriptions in the onPause I would have

```
override fun onPause() {
    super.onPause()
    presenter?.unsubscribeAll()
}
```
and put it in a base activity
